"P2931512997" "You can be rather convincing!"
// DetailString :
"P1713520588" "After thouroughly intimidating the Carnival Mask Tender, she finally agrees to make you a Carnival Master Mask.  Evidently, she's only one of 3 people who even knows how they're made, but she's never made one herself.  Here's hoping it actually works."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1496596075" "Everybody knows what the Carnival of Shadows' masks do.  In short: the wearer of the master mask draws power from those wearing other lesser masks.  Not to mention the wearer of the master mask can see through the eyes of everyone on that psychic network.  You definitely want in on that.  Perhaps you can <i>convince</i> one of these mask makers in the nearby mask making facility to build you one of these master masks."
// AcceptString :
"P3771392810" "Convince the Carnival to build you a master mask."
// SendOffString :
"P3490311532" "Considering how tight lipped the Carnival members have been in the past about anything to do with their organization, you doubt they're just going to 'fess up right away.  You'll likely need to be <i>very</i> convincing."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P185574557" "Get a Carnival Master Mask"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3366034246" "A Carnival master mask isn't going to just present itself.  You better head off to complete your scheme."
