// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_03 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - BooksClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2054168953" "Recovered School Books"
// DetailString :
"P3115185469" "In the Rogue Isles, books like these are fairly uncommon, which makes them valuable.  You're pretty sure someone is working behind the scenes to make sure these books don't make it into the hands of the downtrodden, poorly educated masses."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - EmergencySuppliesClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3704225378" "Recovered Emergency Supplies"
// DetailString :
"P3197180957" "These boxes of supplies will likely only be valuable to those in very dire circumstances.  Fortunately (or unfortunately) these circumstances are quite common in the Rogue Isles."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1370937178" "What is Flambeaux thinking?  Does she think this will actually end well?  There might have been a time where you'd take pity on this girl, but that time has passed.  This plan of hers is just really stupid... and you're going to show her the flaws in it and personally benefit from her foolishness."
// AcceptString :
"P646113143" "Defeat Flambeaux and steal the supplies."
// SendOffString :
"P1567105079" "Knowing Flambeaux, she didn't plan everything out completely.  Thus, you're pretty sure that with all the attention she's gathering for herself, she won't notice you sneaking in and undoing her work.  That is, until you go in and bring the fight to her.  You know that these books and supplies are unlikely to be worth much, but there are probably some people who could use them."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3449607864" "Steal the Supplies"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P187572443" "Flambeaux needs to be taught to think her plans through a bit more.  You plan to do just that."
// TaskTitle :
"P2846080994" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Filmed Announcement</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4027485646" "The clanging of cybernetic limbs: check!  Bad techno music: check!  The Freakshow are here in force."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1450291648" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Filmed Announcement</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You almost feel bad taking down Flambeaux...almost.  She really needed to be taught a lesson.  Now you need to figure out what you'll do with crates upon crates of books and supplies."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3619611073" "Flambeaux and Freakshow confirmed.<em t=3>Got it, we'll fall back until reinforcements arrive."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3606344645" "Uhh, {HeroName} confirmed as well!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3777773897" "<em t=2>Right, call in the reinforcements."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1180622683" "<em t=1>Command, we're going to need to need those reinforcements sooner rather than later."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P1606485468" "Blast Furnace"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1212356797" "Let me in there!<em t=2>Your boss Flambeaux has crossed the line."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2663816632" "{HeroName}!  Give me a hand here, would ya?  I think we both want the same thing."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1422733490" "<em t=1>Forget it, chump!  Why don't you just head back to Paragon City."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2825895314" "Another cape?  You've got to be kidding me."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P3964907925" "I don't care what you do with those supplies as long as you don't destroy them.<em t=2>The oppressed people of the Rogue Isles deserve a chance."
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P3094809541" "A little hand here."
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P2724641317" "Thanks."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P1213919057" "Uh.  Where did you go?"

