"P2143675873" "When WSPDR finally did show up to where Flambeaux was threatening to destroy those worthless supplies, all they found was a mostly empty warehouse with a bunch of unconscious Freakshow."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL8-9_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - BookSearch 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2778899469" "Desdemona's Parting Words"
// DetailString :
"P2846507703" "The Seeds of Destruction were an elaborate plan to trap Desdemona for use in a ritual by the Circle of Thorns. Her parting words before being teleported away to a hospital were to destroy the Book of Kantikos.  You have other ideas in mind for it."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - BookKantikos 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P230897005" "The Book of Kantikos"
// DetailString :
"P2796732149" "As you open the book, the runes marking the pages begin to swirl with dark magics.  Again, you toss it away just in time to avoid the sorcerous explosion.  Your chances of learning its secrets are now forever lost to you."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1794516759" "The power those seeds contain would allow you to do all manner of... Interesting things.  However, the first step will be to get them out of the hands of the Circle of Thorns and into yours.  Once you've found the source of their creation, you could really go to town with these.  And by town, you're thinking Paragon City... or maybe even bigger!"
// AcceptString :
"P2626528342" "Track down the cultists and take their magical seeds!"
// SendOffString :
"P1750272328" "The best place to start looking for the cultists is likely within one of their old temples. And you know exactly where to find one. Head off in that direction and rip those vessels of destructive magic from their zealous hands!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P481637939" "Find the source of the seeds."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3407863148" "You still need to track down the source of where these seeds are coming from.  Once you've found where the Circle of Thorns cultists are creating them, take the seeds for your own."
// TaskTitle :
"P3632089475" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Seeds of Destruction</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3058439099" "This seems like a good place to start looking for more of those seeds.  You can hear these guys chanting up a storm down the myriad hallways of these decrept tunnels. Let's hope you can find the seeds before the cultists find you."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3263979975" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Seeds of Destruction</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The seeds of destruction were nothing more than a lure for Desdemona to walk into the Circle's lair.  Even though you found the book used to create the seeds, that too was booby trapped.  Ultimately, you were able to take out your frustrations on that turncoat, Desdemona, so at least the day wasn't all bad."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1062123591" "<shout>We've caught her!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3509258508" "<shout>Beware!  She's brought more with her!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3987860181" "<shout>Gather the rest!  She's here!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3638897958" "Desdemona"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1581830719" "{HeroName}!  Are you working for the Circle of Thorns?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3080449025" "Well, if you are, we're not letting you get away with spreading those seeds of destruction around."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1621969901" "Where is the summoning book you're using, {HeroName}?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3947410373" "I know of the ritual you used, and I won't stand by watching you corrupt that magic for your own twisted purposes!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P955681354" "Odd... You act as if you weren't the one behind this."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3853469499" "What's going on here?! Are you part of this or not?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P2182648596" "The book of Kantikos... Find it... And destroy it."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P261960767" "And now for the rest of you twisted cultists!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - DefeatDesdemona 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P869778529" "Defeat the Summoner responsible for the seeds"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2707785455" "You learn how the seeds are being made."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2592118967" "It's because {HeroName} isn't, my dear. It was a trap laid out for you!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P13496511" "However, your friend can die as well."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3649103839" "Foolish summoner... The seeds were made to draw you to us!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2537555659" "Kill {HeroName} first, then capture Desdemona for tonight's ritual!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4074281604" "You fool!  What did you do!?  She got away!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4189605995" "You shall pay the price for interfering with our plans!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3325355014" "All of our work for nothing!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P634051086" "Since you know about the book, you'll have to die."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - DestroyBook 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// ModelDisplayName :
"P2234362005" "Arcane Chest"
// Description :
"P3741619510" "Find where the Book of Kantikos is being kept"
// InteractBeginString :
"P3356692616" "you search through the chest for the Book."
// InteractCompleteString :
"P1861785867" "You find the Book of Kantikos..."
// InteractActionString :
"P493485206" "Searching for the Book"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3464238604" "You found the Book of Kantikos."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P2049989413" "It seems the seeds of destruction were only created to lure Dedesmona into a trap.  You may have lost the book, but at least you got to beat up that turncoat... And some cultists at the same time!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P586498300" "Hey look, it's {HeroName}.  That's the one who beat up Desdemona AND the Circle of Thorns in one fell swoop!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_04 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - DesdemonaClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3581085886" "Desdemona's Thanks"
// DetailString :
"P3292753383" "Before the weakened Desdemona ran off, she said she owed you a major favor.  You'll have to remember to take her up on her offer next time you're in a pinch."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3972523139" "These seeds might be too dangerous for even someone like you.  Small and unassuming, anyone could come across them without noticing what kind of danger they're in.  You're not so much concerned about other people being victim of them but rather you running into another one.<br><br>Perhaps it would be best if you tracked down these Circle of Thorns cultists and put a stop to whatever their scheme is!"
// AcceptString :
"P1933785985" "Stop the Circle from creating more of the seeds of destruction."
// SendOffString :
"P1780860040" "You have a pretty good idea where to find the ones responsible for these strange seeds.  If your hunch is right, you'll likely find them in the act of creating more of these deadly little bombs.<br><br>Find some clues as to how they're making them, then take out those crazies!"
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3600799364" "Destroy the Seeds!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1298916341" "You still need to take care of the Circle of Thorns plot to plant the seeds of destruction around the Isles."
// TaskTitle :
"P325300716" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Seeds of Destruction</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1189903335" "As you enter, you hear a mysterious voice in your mind - 'Whoever you are... Help me... I've stopped the cultists... But they've... Caught me...'.  Sounds like you weren't the only one with a mind to beat the daylights out of these cultists."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2054458861" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Seeds of Destruction</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Desdemona, demon summoner turned hero, beat you to the punch.  Although you might see that as a bad thing, she was the one who did all the work.  All you had to do was lift a finger, and now she owes you a favor."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2509526624" "The Low Chanter is on his way to... Acquire his prize."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1881040439" "And it looks like we have another prize for our lord."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3102028650" "It's good to know that she's been subdued."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2344174499" "<shout>He comes!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1698300016" "<shout>You delay the inevitable!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1455068154" "<shout>Submit and your death will be quick!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2785194057" "<shout>A prize for the Low Chanter!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3875552930" "<shout>The bride can not escape!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P587585996" "<shout>Your death will be painful!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3779577524" "The Low Chanter"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2900060125" "My bride... She has been taken from me?  I feel it."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P4184563913" "You will pay for your audacity!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P1170733051" "You followed my trail of seeds, did you not?"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P786241143" "They were not intended for you, fool."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1083359873" "<shout>I am done with this... COME TO ME!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P4015765497" "You dare cross one who has mastery over death?"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P3533707583" "You.. Can not... Kill me... Forever..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P3773610762" "And now your soul will be mine!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - DefeatAmbushBoss 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
