"P1578620623" "You've stopped the Low Chanter."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1343681466" "<shout>We come to aid you, master!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4222897965" "How could I have been so reckless?  Such an obvious trap."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3594218085" "{HeroName}?<em t=1>Were you lured by the seeds as well?<em t=2>It's all a ruse!  Help me and we can work together."
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2064685843" "So predictable.  <em t=1>Curious as ever.  Now, your soul will serve as the perfect catalyst to--<em t=2>Shh, I think I heard something!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1166277979" "What are you doing here?<em t=2>Destroy them!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3459019140" "High Priest Gathemedes"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P2226606284" "Thank you, {HeroName}.  I certainly didn't expect for you to show up."
// Script Variable SayOnArrival :
"P338693551" "I'm going to make a run for it.  You should likely do the same."
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P2954335710" "Find the mysterious voice"

