// ExitStringSuccess :
"P170245562" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Exotic Armor Schematics</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>True to his word, the Arachnos Engineer showed you where he stashed the Rikti armor blueprints.  It the end, you're not sure how useful this armor will be in actuality, but it will at least make a decent trophy."
