"P3326279594" "You've extracted a Power Nodule from its container.  This small device is used to power Reichsman's empowerment chambers.  Without it, he'll be severely weakened."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1863463979" "The 5th Column are a blight.  Their silly fascist agendas to take over the world, how cliche.  Wouldn't it be a shame if you were to infiltrate the base where these Power Nodules are stored and take them for yourself?  Perhaps that'll teach the 5th Column to conduct their business in the Rogue Isles."
// AcceptString :
"P782286412" "Steal 5th Column Power Nodules."
// SendOffString :
"P778851395" "They're likely skulking around in one of their former hideouts, licking their wounds.  You've got a good idea where you can find them.  Track them down and steal their Power Nodules."
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1375851156" "You have yet to steal the 5th Column Power Nodules.  The possibilities of such a concentrated power source boggles the mind!"
// TaskTitle :
"P639314073" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Classified Mission Directive</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

