// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// DetailString :
"P3468824448" "This painting is clearly the base leader's favorite.  It looks like it is dusted daily and has an incredibly expensive looking frame."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - PowerNodule 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// DetailString :
"P3132767775" "You've destroyed a Power Nodule.  This device is used to power Reichsman's empowerment chambers.  Without it, he'll be severely weakened."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3409026118" "Those Power Nodules can't be allowed to be used to empower the 5th Column's leader, Reichsman.  If these were to fall into the wrong hands, the results could be catastrophic.  It's best if you infiltrate that 5th Column base and destroy their Power Nodules <i>and</i> loot the place of any valuables.  After all, the 5th Column are notorious collectors of priceless pieces of art."
// AcceptString :
"P677675696" "Destroy the Power Nodules and loot the base."
// SendOffString :
"P2066267418" "Those Power Nodules need to go!  No good deed should go without a reward, so you'll help yourself to any valuables within the 5th Column base.  Sounds like a win-win situation.  You make the Reichsman suffer and you get some priceless art."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2929568665" "Loot the 5th Column Base"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1276790547" "There's a base loaded with priceless pieces of art that are practically begging to be yours.  Oh, and there's also the matter of destroying those Power Nodules.  You should probably do that as well."
// TaskTitle :
"P4009701111" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Classified Mission Directive</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3172597252" "You can hear orders being barked over a loudspeaker and klaxons sounding around you.  Evidently your entrance hasn't gone unnoticed."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4251095333" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Classified Mission Directive</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>That was satisfying.  Not only did you liberate a number of priceless paintings, you also destroyed the Power Nodules.  That'll definitely leave the 5th Column reeling for awhile."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3302210375" "There's an intruder alert!<em t=2>Keep a sharp eye out!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P132256380" "Oh great!  It's {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3788490054" "<em t=3>Looks clear so far--wait, I think I heard something!"

