// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - OverdriveDownClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2586582545" "Battle Cry"
// DetailString :
"P3831294229" "Overdrive falls to her knees and is teleported away to safety before you can deliver a finishing blow.  In the distance you hear a furious battle cry and the roars of a horde of demons."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1953701339" "It's hard to pass up a situation like this.  Overdrive is practically being given to you thanks to the Family tipping you off that she was in the Rogue Isles.  There's the small matter of dealing with her bodyguards, but you figure a warmup is in order before taking on Overdrive."
// AcceptString :
"P926666529" "Take out Overdrive!"
// SendOffString :
"P675056441" "Overdrive is currently investigating an abandoned office for Family activity with a large group of Longbow.  Now's your chance to swoop in and take her out."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1972891733" "Take out Overdrive"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3260213037" "Overdrive is investigating an abandoned office nearby.  Now's your chance!  Get in there and take out Overdrive."
// TaskTitle :
"P1229374496" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>This is How She Dies</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P590576760" "You can hear the echoes of voices from deep within the warehouse.  You hear a woman arguing with someone else."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2908980529" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>This is How She Dies</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color deepskyblue><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>That was unexpected!  You managed to not only take out Overdrive, but Desdemona as well.  When word of this gets around, the Rogue Isles will fear your name even more than usual."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P4005072348" "I'm not so sure I trust her.<em t=3>I know, but still.  I mean she summons de--wait, what was that?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3990334253" "Oh great.  We've got villain troubles!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P4274207284" "<em t=1>Positron vouched for her personally.  I think she'll be a great help."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1900839643" "Overdrive"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1850871752" "Okay, look guys.<em t=1>You need to trust me on this.  Desdemona is our ally.<em t=2>I sent her away so we could talk ab--did you hear something?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2973134623" "What?<em t=1>{HeroName}?<em t=1>I'm not sure what you're doing here, but I intend to stop you!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P567090969" "You've got quite the reputation in the Rogue Isles, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3542823192" "I got sloppy, I should have prepared for this."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2658374195" "I admit, you're powerful.<em t=2>But, I'm not through with you yet!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2718746997" "I-I can't give up!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4271545722" "Desdemona!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P952748979" "You're not as tough as they say, {HeroName}."

