// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3897827113" "I won't let you get away with this."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1940088518" "You're a lot stronger than the Longbow reports made out."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P1331736787" "Overdrive, I'm sorry."

