// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_07 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - DesdemonaClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2260873735" "Desdemona's Warning"
// DetailString :
"P3138309004" "Desdemona tells you that she's been working with Overdrive and Longbow to investigate a Family crime spree that began in Paragon City.  They found themselves in the Rogue Isles, stepped on some toes, and now Arachnos and the Family are actively hunting them down."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P294905296" "The Family wants Overdrive killed.  They themselves would have a heck of a time doing that, though; she's no joke.  They'll likely hire mercenaries and other villains--like yourself--to do it.  Your hope is that by warning her you might earn a favor that you'll be able to call in."
// AcceptString :
"P2832252440" "Warn Overdrive!"
// SendOffString :
"P992192447" "The Family has a lot of resources to throw at their problems.  It wouldn't be out of the question to expect other big hitters in there.  You're hoping she's grateful enough to owe you a favor."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P553806867" "Warn Overdrive"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2414512330" "Overdrive has to be warned of the Family's plot to kill her."
// TaskTitle :
"P1546483763" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>This is How She Dies</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P796095796" "You fear it might be too late.  You overhear Arachnos troops patrolling the place.  They must have overheard the Family message as well!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1992394399" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>This is How She Dies</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You managed to wade through the mess that was created when the call went out to kill Overdrive.  You managed to save her life, which is something you'll bring up if she ever tries to take you to the slammer.<br><br>Surely that's something those do-gooders will keep in mind, right?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3448157417" "Hah!  The Family, what a joke!<em t=2>Lord Recluse will be pleased when we present him with both Overdrive and Desdemona!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3125099022" "{HeroName}!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P875521601" "<em t=1>Their bounty on the heroes was laughable!"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3148654800" "We won't let you steal our glory."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4127058909" "You are making a horrible mistake.<em t=2>I don't want to harm you, but I will if you don't release me."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P191334274" "Now you see what I mean?<em t=1>{HeroName} is here and they're not likely to go easy on you."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P897330248" "Operative Wilkins"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P288456987" "<em t=1>A mistake?  No.  I think not.<em t=2>Lord Recluse was quite clear when he said he wanted Overdrive and any of her hero friends brought before him for judgment.<em t=4>We'll have to remember to thank the Family for their--who's there?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2419662209" "This is our lucky day.<em t=1>We nab Overdrive, Desdemona and {HeroName}!<em t=2>Lord Recluse might even make me a patron!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P2454752267" "Well done, {HeroName}. Thank you.<em t=2>You're here to warn Overdrive?<em t=3>A bit late for that, but I think we can still help her.<em t=4>Be careful though, Arachnos has hired some mercenaries to help bring in Overdrive."
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P2442376785" "Going to need a little help here."
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P339614867" "Thanks, let's continue."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P552224347" "These old offices are like labyrinths!  I'm lost."
// Script Variable WaveShout :
"P4286381209" "<shout>{HeroName} is getting away with our prize!  Attack!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - RescueDesdemona 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3118086892" "<color orange>Recruit Desdemona (Optional)</color>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1896481890" "Look, Hollow Point.  It doesn't have to be this wa-"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3064344754" "Hollow Point"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1649185797" "<em t=1>No, you look!<em t=2>It does have to be this way.  You've interfered with my plans too many times.<em t=4>Lord Recluse wants you alive, but I can't take that risk.<em t=5>Any last words?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3046434352" "<em t=1>{HeroName}?<em t=2>Odd last wo--wait a minute!<em t=3>It's really {HeroName}!  To arms!  To arms!"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P1415552581" "{HeroName}, I'm truly surprised to see you here.  You're here to warn me?<em t=2>A little late, but your timing on saving me couldn't be better.<em t=4>I'm exhausted and pretty beat up.  I'm afraid I won't be much use to you in a fight.<em t=5>Get me out of here and I'll put in a good word for you, should you ever decide to come to Paragon City."
// Script Variable SayOnArrival :
"P1158709365" "As I promised, Desdemona and I will spread the word.  Keep doing good things, {HeroName}!<em t=2>It's not too late to turn over a new leaf."
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P1880887930" "{HeroName}!  They're after me."
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P3018459207" "Thanks, I wish I could be of more use.<em t=2>They really did a number on me."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P999913641" "Oh no.  I'm lost again.  {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable RescueObjectiveText :
"P726188482" "Find Overdrive"
// Script Variable LeadToObjectiveText :
"P3615340830" "Lead Overdrive to safety"

