// Dialog :
"P442823646" "You found the stolen tech, but it seems like Doc Quantum was expecting this!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3843865572" "Doc Quantum"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2054556801" "You performed brilliantly in my experiment, {HeroName}. I think I will require more study of your brain - surely you would not mind parting with it?"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P2168683409" "The base is on full alert now, {HeroName}. You won't get away."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2663179075" "I wonder now, why did you do it? To stop me from getting the girl? "
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1655850892" "Or are you just acting out of your own self-interest? You're a magnificent specimen, that is one thing for sure..."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P333377953" "If only the world were as interesting as you, {HeroName}...!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4196401684" "Even with my defeat...I've obtained valuable research..."

