// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL8-9_Task_09 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - CommanderID 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1374956888" "Ruined Commander ID"
// DetailString :
"P1998167704" "You ripped the commander's ID from their body after you beat them down. The ID has traces of your attack on it - this should catch the attention of those Longbow back in Paragon."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SpiderHelm 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1761099769" "Bane Spider Helm"
// DetailString :
"P1565371397" "You ripped off this helm from the Bane Spider you defeated. It's a bit more roughed up than the helm you already found, which will be perfect to show to Longbow."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Scheme 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1716441071" "Longbow's Reaction"
// DetailString :
"P2767739727" "You activate a live video feed to one of Longbow's headquarters in Paragon City. Several of the higher ups were gathered around to listen to what you had to say. <br><br>After speaking for a few moments, you displayed to the Longbow the ID tag of their commander and the destroyed helmet of the Bane Spider they hoped to save. You turned and walked away from the video feed, overhearing the members of Longbow shouting furiously at you.<br><br>Time to blow up this base."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P297791942" "Longbow's presence in the Rogue Isles has done nothing but cause irritation after irritation - counting this latest one with the Bane Spiders. After doing some more investigating on the matter, you're able to piece together that the Bane Spider's link breaking was most likely caused by some agents within Longbow - they have had plans before to do this.<br><br>Which means they'll have Bane Spider turncoats at that Longbow base. Not that it'll matter - from the videos you've stolen, the base is already in ruins. Time for you to finish what Arachnos started and kick Longbow out of your turf.<br><br>However, just destroying the base won't be enough. You'll have to make an example out of the higher ups there. You're going to find key people there and make sure all of Longbow - and Paragon - know that you took them down."
// AcceptString :
"P343064821" "Destroy the Longbow base!"
// SendOffString :
"P3940889040" "You make your way to the Longbow base, ready to finish off the job Arachnos started - in a manner that they could never hope to replicate."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P333366723" "Destroy the Longbow Base!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1781017002" "That base is still active - for the moment."
// TaskTitle :
"P3403433520" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Bloody Bane Spider Helmet</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2025894123" "You go through the blown up entrance in the sewers to enter the Longbow base. You can hear them trying to repair their base - time to stop that."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3038985154" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Bloody Bane Spider Helmet</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You get to a safe distance from the base before setting it to explode. Plumes of smoke rise from the ruins of the Longbow base, and they know exactly who did it. Good. They now have a face to associate with their nightmares."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3197860152" "Base Commander"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1099492998" "Get this base up and running now! We can't risk a breach like this in the Isles!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2708765149" "{HeroName}! Look alive, people!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - LongbowCommander 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P4025681981" "Defeat the Longbow Commander!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P1010261821" "You beat down the Longbow Commander and took their ruined ID tag."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1531197990" "Rescued Bane Spider"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3908282676" "Freedom...it's so close. I almost forgot what it's like. But...do I really still have to take up the fight against Arachnos...?"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P799242483" "You. {HeroName}. It's because of people like you that the world is in this state. I'll take you down to earn my freedom!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - BaneSpider 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2278007546" "Defeat the rescued Bane Spider!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P4108240990" "You beat down the Bane Spider and took his helm - that makes two today!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Computer 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
