// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Bombs 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// ModelDisplayName :
"P2020931920" "Bomb"
// Description :
"P2205234484" "Plant the explosives to blow up the base!"
// InteractBeginString :
"P3693888985" "Arming the explosive..."
// InteractInterruptedString :
"P2557807414" "You have been interrupted!"
// InteractCompleteString :
"P1353955183" "The bomb has been set!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P736237483" "The look on Longbow's faces over the video feed was priceless. Now to get out and blow up the place."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P1856189824" "Someone posted a video of {HeroName} beating down a Longbow agent! I...I can't stop watching it...is that bad?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_09 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P1542616577" "<color orange>The captured Bane Spider looks up to you, his armor battered in. Crey obviously has captured him by force.</color><br><br>You're {HeroName}, right? ...so...you're here to bring me over to Arachnos, I take it. Fine...I can't fight anymore. Bring me to my fate."
// Answer Text :
"P648595989" "Looks like today is your lucky day. You're going to Longbow."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P37567343" "<color orange>The Bane Spider looks up at you in shock.</color><br><br>Longbow?! R-really? Thank you...thank you!"
// Answer Text :
"P3387837221" "Calm down, it's only because Longbow offered more for you."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P183591282" "Alright...okay...so...what's next?"
// Answer Text :
"P2347908753" "I'm going to contact the agent from Longbow now to come get you."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P2130491353" "<color orange>You take out your communicator to send a message out to Longbow. A man named Agent G replies, saying that he is on his way. However, he says that there is an Arachnos squad breaking into the warehouse shortly. You'll have to deal with them before he can get in to make the trade.</color><br><br>I'm sorry {HeroName}, but I won't be able to help you out against those Arachnos.<br><br>I'll find a good place to hide...good luck...!"
// Answer Text :
"P352363378" "...great."
// Page InformationPage4 Text :
"P1817064269" "<color orange>The Bane Spider runs to hide inside of one of the crates. You can hear Arachnos already bearing down on the warehouse!"
// Answer Text :
"P2775569793" "The things that get in the way of making cash in this place..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - AgentG 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P2661522647" "<color orange>A Longbow agent stands before you, holding a suitcase in his right hand.</color><br><br>Hello, {HeroName}. I've heard a lot about you. I trust you have the...package we're looking for?"
// Answer Text :
"P3161123164" "As long as you've got the money."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3141921109" "<color orange>The agent hands you the suitcase. You open it up and count the money in there - it's the exact amount that Longbow promised.</color><br><br>I trust that we have a deal then? "
// Answer Text :
"P3251882114" "We have a deal. Your man is in a crate in the back."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P2595349959" "<color orange>The agent gives you a nod and quickly walks off to retrieve the Bane Spider.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1456081233" "At least that's over with."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4196778967" "Some Bane Spiders acting up says one thing to you - opportunity. Longbow and Arachnos are looking for any of them and they're both offering top dollar for them. <br><br>Unfortunately for Arachnos, Longbow happens to have a bigger paycheck to spend for the Bane Spiders.<br><br>You do some investigating and get in touch with certain contacts to find out that Crey has already located one of the Bane Spiders and is currently holding him hostage in one of their warehouses. <br><br> It looks like you've got your lead, at least. Crey has enough money as it is - it's time to spread the wealth."
// AcceptString :
"P301819220" "Sell the Bane Spider to Longbow!"
// SendOffString :
"P1586000521" "You head off to find the Bane Spider. It's lucky for you that Crey is keeping him nice and cozy until you show up..."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1531002068" "Find the Bane Spider!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3051117569" "Crey might be upset, but what are they going to do? Sue you?"
// TaskTitle :
"P1092219605" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Bloody Bane Spider Helmet</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P5818890" "The Crey warehouse is on full alert. They're ready and waiting for Arachnos to come get their man."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3334312307" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Bloody Bane Spider Helmet</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You casually walk out of the Crey warehouse with the suitcase full of money - courtesy of Longbow. Not too bad of a payday, if you do say so yourself."
// Script Variable NPC_DIALOG_NAME :
"P693874779" "Agent G"

