// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL8-9_Task_10 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P112281596" "Silent Blade once stood for something.  She would eliminate targets for an organization and with a greater purpose.  Now she's willing to take out anyone for a price regardless of the consequences.  Heroes, Villains, those that walk in between those defined roles, they're all fair game.<br><br>It's time to beat some sense into her and make a fortune while doing it."
// AcceptString :
"P643104840" "Take out Silent Blade!"
// SendOffString :
"P2777092099" "You've got Silent Blade's location.  The hunt is on.  You get to take down one of the world's most notorious assassins <i>and</i> bring the hurt to Longbow.  It sounds like today might be a good day after all."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2764803883" "Defeat Silent Blade"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3017865388" "You have a mark that still needs to be eliminated."
// TaskTitle :
"P2281007628" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Hand Delivered Note</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2967050413" "Heavily armored bootfalls can be heard through the dilapidated halls of this old office building.  Sounds like Longbow beat you here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2478890612" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Hand Delivered Note</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Silent Blade was as cunning and ruthless as you've heard, but in the end, she was no match for you.  Once again you're approached by the shadowy figure, who hands you your payment before leaping away to the nearest rooftop."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P4107215131" "Longbow Officer"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3710821104" "Quickly, Officer Tasset has informed me that they've found Silent Blade's location."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1776128842" "Change of plans.  {HeroName} is higher priority."
// Script Variable PET_NAME :
"P4260422440" "Silent Blade"
// Script Variable PET_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P761682228" "<em t=1>I don't think so. You're now my prey!"
// Script Variable PET_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P395465870" "I had a feeling they would send you, {HeroName}.<em t=2>No matter, you'll be my next victim."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P4205408338" "You've given me the perfect opportunity.<em t=2>I'll strike while you're weakened by your fight with Longbow."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1469840589" "Officer Tasset"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P363502767" "We've got you now, Silent Blade!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1170261792" "{HeroName}!  Are they a higher priority target?  Why, I think they are.  Get them!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptFirstHeroBossRescued 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P842965842" "Find Silent Blade"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P922058904" "You've handily defeated Silent Blade."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptSilentBlade 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3129090948" "You defeated Silent Blade."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P4224998810" "Longbow just made {HeroName} their number one wanted criminal.  Wasn't Silent Blade number one yesterday?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_10 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - SilentBladeClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1215350418" "Silent Blade's Surprise"
// DetailString :
"P3530801672" "'You're here to...warn me?  Why on earth would you want to help me?  You would like a truce.  Very well.  This is an odd situation, but...I suppose thanks are in order.  Just know that you've made an enemy of the Whispered Hand.'"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P992814409" "Someday Silent Blade might be hired to eliminate you which would be a complication you'd prefer to avoid if at all possible.  You're presented with an opportunity to make an ally.  Unfortunately, that would likely mean that you're going to anger the Whispered Hand.  Perhaps having Silent Blade as an ally might prevent them from acting against you.  Besides, you and Silent Blade have a lot in common, you'll do just about anything if it'll better your situation and it pays well enough.  You think you'll head out and give her a hand."
// AcceptString :
"P2341187904" "Warn Silent Blade."
// SendOffString :
"P1600163096" "As you head off to the office where Silent Blade is believed to be, you get the feeling that you're being watched by a dozen eyes.  Hopefully Silent Blade will appreciate this gesture. It can never hurt to have more allies in the Rogue Isles."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P869635701" "Warn Silent Blade"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3417090039" "Silent Blade still needs to be warned of the impending danger."
// TaskTitle :
"P1849403262" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Hand Delivered Note</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2433016407" "You hope the messenger was right about this place."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P957449617" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Hand Delivered Note</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>There was a feeling that you were being watched for good reason.  After rescuing Silent Blade you were assaulted by a number of the Whispered Hand's assassins.  Just as you hoped, Silent Blade has agreed to form a truce with you.  She swore a blood oath to not take an assassination contract if it involved you as the target."
// Script Variable PET_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3676462784" "This is disappointing.  I was actually hoping for a challenge."
// Script Variable PET_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P291191221" "{HeroName}?  Have you come for me too?"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P1567337917" "What?  You're here to...warn me?  Why would you do that?"
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P1164421489" "<shout>Hey! {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1042941464" "Operative Tassett"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2286216609" "I'm taking you down Silent Blade."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P271839106" "You!  Change of plans, engage {HeroName}.  They're a higher priority target."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2464212578" "The Colonel must be further into this makeshift base!  Let's be off!"
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P837500721" "But she needed to be brought to justice!"

