// Task - AM_Vil_SL8-9_Task_11 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ShockTreatmentClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3695243575" "Two Like Minds"
// DetailString :
"P4077955626" "After recruiting Shock Treatment's help she tells you:<br><br>'Oh goodie, I really just wanted to get into the party, but these goons wouldn't let me in.  I just wanted to slap around these heroes who've given me so much trouble in the past.  You understand, don't you?  Be a dear and take me along, it should be good fun.'"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P1091429043" "You don't rightly care who those heroes are.  It's always a wise idea to eliminate your enemies when the opportunity presents itself.  This might be some sort of trap, but you don't care.  The bait is just too sweet."
// AcceptString :
"P3107587773" "Eliminate weakened heroes."
// SendOffString :
"P1762059207" "You take note of the location specified by Doc Quantum and set off to beat those heroes silly.  Moral experiment or not, this sounds like too much fun to pass up.  You'll show Doc Quantum your moral compass points in whichever direction suits you at the time.<br><br>From what you know of Mangle, he's likely aligned himself with many likeminded individuals who wish to overthrow the government.  It's not uncommon for him to recruit people from groups like the Council."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P292488603" "Eliminate the Heroes"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P576774134" "You can't wait to find and pummel those heroes silly."
// TaskTitle :
"P767386744" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Just How Evil Are You?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1006424974" "Sewers!  Why must they always hide in the blasted sewers?!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P392882829" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Just How Evil Are You?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Well that was satisfying.  Those are a couple of heroes that won't be causing you any problems for quite some time."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P163889391" "I hope I get to <i>interrogate</i> them this time around."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1232527341" "Oh crud, it's {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P688724409" "<em t=2>And by interrogate you mean mercilessly beat on for half an hour for fun?"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_NAME :
"P327788581" "Shock Treatment"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1245451884" "I just want to hurt them a little, boys.<em t=2>Won't you please let me in?<em t=2>I promise I'll be good.<em t=2>Okay, that's a lie."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2385811114" "{HeroName}!<em t=2>Goodie, how about we get these party poopers out of the way and we move onto the main event!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3581824003" "Militia Leader"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P475115824" "<em t=1>Listen you lunatic, I've already told you twice.<em t=3>I won't say it again."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2576230722" "Men, let's show these dolts what we do to intruders."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P156830079" "Oh hi, so good to see you, {HeroName}.  Let's cause some mayhem!"
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P3854685424" "You boys are no fun at all."
