// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - DesdemonaClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P717877724" "A Dubious Desdemona"
// DetailString :
"P2649323074" "This ex-villain turned over a new leaf and became one of Paragon City's finest.  She's clearly here after the same thing you are.  Well, maybe for a different reason, but she wants the same thing.  So, perhaps a temporary truce is in order."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - HeroClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1532736736" "A Surprised Hero"
// DetailString :
"P1222415107" "The subdued hero thanked you for saving him and swore he would spread the good word about you in Paragon City."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P924917433" "Beating up harmless people has never been your thing.  There's no satisfaction in doing something that requires so little effort.  Not to mention these heroes could spread the word about you in Paragon City, plant the seeds as it were.  Heck, they might even reward you for your help."
// AcceptString :
"P42233789" "Get those heroes out of there."
// SendOffString :
"P3496358948" "It's all about looking out for number one.  Sometimes that means making connections, building alliances.  The fewer enemies you have, the less you have to watch your back.  Helping out these heroes will definitely give you an edge."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3823238965" "Help Subdued Heroes"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P97391033" "You still need to rescue those heroes... connections don't grow on trees."
// TaskTitle :
"P972642901" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Just How Evil Are You?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1243133421" "Hopefully you're not too late.  You hear a bone cracking impact followed by a long muffled moan."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3937727402" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Just How Evil Are You?</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Those guys were in truly bad shape when you found them, but you managed to lead them to safety.  They were adequately appreciative for your aid and promised to tell others about your deeds."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3849762485" "You're in way over your head here.<em t=3>I won't be outnumbered for much longer, boys."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2712628340" "{HeroName}?<em t=2>Either help me or stay out of my way."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1641215298" "<em t=1>Hah, I think not!  You're outnumbered and outclassed."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3830026576" "Bah!  The numbers appear to be shifting in your favor."
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P822745112" "I'll spare you the preachiness, {HeroName}.<em t=2>I don't normally work with villains, but we have a common cause.<em t=2>Even if you're doing this for the wrong reasons."
// Script Variable SayOnRecapture :
"P3925477234" "Ugh, they have me.  There's too many of them!"
// Script Variable SayOnRerescue :
"P2834975013" "...Thanks."
// Script Variable SayOnStranded :
"P901305447" "...Typical."

