"P1556789116" "Inside the body bag you find a deceased villain of the Rogue Isles.  You don't recognize the villain. Sadly there's nothing of any value inside."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - MissThystleClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2852524232" "Miss Thystle Automaton"
// DetailString :
"P1723736455" "At first you were wondering what Miss Thystle was doing here, but quickly you realized you were fighting a mechanical copy."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - DoppelgangerClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3052971672" "Ominous Tag"
// DetailString :
"P4273832445" "A small tag on the inside of this body bag has your name on it.  Evidently Nemesis has reserved a special place for you here."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3758011290" "You don't really care how big of a threat you are, in fact you'd prefer to not be on that list at all.  It'd be easier to operate undetected in the Rogue Isles that way.  What you do care about is what Nemesis is up to, and what valuables might be stashed away in that warehouse."
// AcceptString :
"P983637224" "Investigate and loot warehouse."
// SendOffString :
"P3289623984" "If Nemesis has successfully eliminated villains or heroes and brought them back to this warehouse, then perhaps their tools and equipment haven't been picked clean.  There might be some incredibly powerful devices and artifacts there.  You head off to the coordinates listed in the Jaeger's computer."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P405708890" "Investigate Nemesis Warehouse"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P4205726318" "Somewhere in Grandville is a warehouse ripe for the picking, just loaded with goodies.  Or so you hope."
// TaskTitle :
"P2670089939" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Broken Nemesis Jaeger</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1582317860" "This place is as quiet as a grave.  While that is ominous, you hope that there are a few bodies to pilfer artifacts and devices from."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3027114794" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>A Broken Nemesis Jaeger</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You didn’t recognize any of the fallen heroes or villains; they were probably low on that Nemesis threat list.  Unfortunately there was nothing of any value there, and you were lucky to escape with your life as you were assaulted by automaton copies of both Miss Thystle and yourself."

