// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - DemonicManualClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3457927402" "Pile of Demonic Tomes"
// DetailString :
"P1496254619" "Inside the chest you discover half a dozen tomes that are identical to the one that lead you to the Taper of the Frozen Flame."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - TaperClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2176070320" "Taper of the Frozen Flame"
// DetailString :
"P2928740878" "At first glance, the Taper of the Frozen Flame looks like a highly ornate, but otherwise normal candle.  But, upon examining it closer you can tell it's not made of wax and is ever so slightly translucent.  Holding the taper in your hand chills you to your very soul."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - ThesaedesClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3514691774" "Thesaedes's Plan"
// DetailString :
"P705581903" "After interrogating Thesaedes he reveals that his plan was to make several copies of a tome that detailed the power of the Taper of the Frozen Flame and litter them throughout the Rogue Isles.  He says this was done to lure a powerful magic-based villain who could manipulate cold that they could use to harness the power of the taper.  They planned to use this power to cover the surface in a perpetual winter."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P311418560" "This artifact's potential isn't missed by your keen eye.  With it you could...well the possibilities are nearly endless!  Plus, it's best to snatch up that artifact before someone else does.  Should this fall into the hands of the unworthy, who knows what would happen."
// AcceptString :
"P505103170" "Take the Taper of the Frozen Flame for yourself!"
// SendOffString :
"P3644688600" "If your suspicions are correct and the Taper of the Frozen Flame is still here, you're about to become a very powerful {Hero.gender=male man|woman}.  The likelihood of someone knowing about the taper is pretty high, so you should prepare yourself for that possibility.  You head off to where you believe the Taper of the Frozen Flame lies."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1182960956" "Recover the Taper"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3918475108" "You still need to recover the Taper of the Frozen Flame before someone else takes it first."
// TaskTitle :
"P3051304011" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Taper Of The Frozen Flame</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
