"P3161408396" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Taper Of The Frozen Flame</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>It wasn't easy, but you now have in your possession an artifact that will greatly amplify the power of someone's ability to manipulate cold.  The villain Polar Shift attempted to thwart you, but she was no match for you."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P941711851" "I wonder if Thesaedes's plan will work."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2980798773" "It worked."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1635712996" "Surely greed will lure them to us.<em t=2>I didn't made 50 copies of that tome and spread them around the Rogue Isles for nothing."
