// IntroString :
"P3512820203" "This Taper of the Frozen Flame's power is incredibly tempting.  You could sell it, or perhaps use it for your own ends.  However, you keep coming back to the same conclusion.  Doing either can only end in catastrophe.  The only solution is to destroy the artifact."
// AcceptString :
"P1888906843" "Destroy this artifact before it falls into the wrong hands."
// SendOffString :
"P3218845966" "If someone with truly ill intentions got their hands on this artifact it could spell the end of everything.  Catastrophes aren't good for business, namely your business of making a name for yourself in the Rogue Isles.  You head off to where you believe the Taper might be."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1217210301" "Destroy the Taper"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P2545374090" "The Taper of the Frozen Flame could still fall into the hands of a very dangerous individual. You need to destroy it before that happens."
// TaskTitle :
"P2259769619" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Taper Of The Frozen Flame</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1702884374" "You hear harmonized chanting and gutteral demonic snarls.  The Circle of Thorns is obviously here too."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1829005950" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Taper of the Frozen Flame</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>The Circle of Thorns was intending to lure villains to their lair to harness their energy to use the power of the Taper of the Frozen Flame.  Not only that, but you were attacked by Polar Shift, who was also after the artifact.  Your gut feeling was right, that artifact needed to be destroyed.  After defeating Polar Shift, she seemed to come to some sort of realization and snuck away in tears."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2271784256" "How long must we wait?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P623843641" "Ah hah!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3044222136" "Soon, I'm sure of it!  A greedy soul will pass through these doors to claim their reward.  We didn’t make copies of those tomes for nothing."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P125753457" "Quickly, subdue them!"

