// Clue - AutomatonPartsClue 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P146910237" "More Flambeauxs?"
// DetailString :
"P2194950280" "After you destroyed this crate, you found out that it was filled with more Flambeaux doppelganger parts.  Exactly what is Flambeaux up to here?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P4243540765" "Flambeaux is a shining example of what a villain should aspire <b>NOT</b> to be.  You're sick and tired of this little twerp showing up and demanding attention.  Infamy is earned by causing some havoc, not by throwing a stupid party and inviting everyone.  Knowing her, she'll be surprised by you showing up and wanting to break up her pointless grab at attention.  How sad."
// AcceptString :
"P4191113727" "Crash Flambeaux's little party."
// SendOffString :
"P797747809" "Flambeaux will probably not see this coming, and you're probably not going to be the only villain in there that wants to see her eliminated.  This fiery little tart needs to be taught a painful lesson today.  Just to discourage her from doing this ever again, you think you'll destroy any other automatons she might have around the warehouse.  You ball up the Flambeax Festival flier, toss it over your shoulder and head out to where it is being held."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2048032086" "Crash the Party"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3342257328" "Flambeaux's party will not likely crash itself.  You need to get over there and cause some damage."
// TaskTitle :
"P2543550761" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Two Too Many Flambeauxs</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2333833369" "The sound of loud electronic music, pounding bass and the clang of cheap cybernetics fills the halls of this old decrepit warehouse.  Sounds like the Freakshow are already here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P4293628466" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Two Too Many Flambeauxs</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You not only taught Flambeaux a very painful lesson, but you've destroyed all her little mechanical toys.  You don't know about everyone else, but you had a great time at this little party."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P741079630" "*klick* Flambeaux.<em t=1>Is.<em t=1>The.<em t=1>Best.<em t=1>Hostess.<em t=1>Ever.  *whirr*"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1636140380" "Welcome.<em t=1>To.<em t=1>The.<em t=1>Party."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1462394257" "*grind* I.  Wholeheartedly.<em t=1>Isn't.<em t=1>Flambeaux.<em t=1>The.<ERROR: CANNOT FIND FLAMBEAUXFLATTERY12.TXT> *clunk*"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1287574925" "<ERROR: CANNOT FIND WELCOME41.TXT, RUNNING AGGRESSIVEDIALOGUE3.TXT INSTEAD> Kill them!  *klink*"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P4269351632" "Let me in or I'll tear your arms off!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P50621513" "If you're after Flambeaux, maybe we...could...work together?"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1584420306" "T3h Cl4W"
