"P1089220311" "Hmm....tempting, but I must decline your offer.<em t=2>Allow me to retort.<em t=1> I think it is I who will tear <i>your</i> arms off."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1617430011" "Hey, let's bounce these party poopers.  Flambeaux didn't want anybody trouble tonight."
