// DetailString :
"P2182601225" "You rescued an automaton that looks just like Flambeaux. It seemed desperate to help the real Flambeaux."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2370746815" "Flambeaux is most likely going to be in a world of trouble.  In an attempt to make everyone love her, she's inadvertently made everyone hate her guts.  Her constant ploys to be the center of attention have made a lot of heroes and villains want to see her go away.  Permanently.  You've got to give her a hand."
// AcceptString :
"P2829762710" "Prevent Flambeaux from getting in trouble."
// SendOffString :
"P2336219651" "Flambeaux annoys the heck out of everyone, including you, but you don't think she deserves to die.  Perhaps you can get through to her that she needs to lay low, back off, and cool it.  Otherwise, she may end up disappearing.  You head off to the location where this party is set to happen."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3163174818" "Rescue Flambeaux"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1250688284" "Flambeaux is likely to end up dead if you don't do something."
// TaskTitle :
"P623844818" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Two Too Many Flambeauxs</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P1663357772" "Loud techno music is interrupted by screams, gunfire and barked orders.  It sounds like Arachnos is here."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2839206584" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Two Too Many Flambeauxs</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>It seems that even Arachnos wanted to take out Flambeaux.  You managed to get her out of there despite all of the Arachnos agents.  She seemed thankful, and you think you might have actually gotten through her thick skull.  Or maybe she was just pretending to listen to you...who knows?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P830017758" "Keep an eye out.<em t=1>Don't let anyone in or out.<em t=2>Flambeaux dies today."
