// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2817100788" "<em t=2>She's playing with some pretty dangerous toys. <em t=2>Toys that Lord Recluse would like to get his hands on."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P166843588" "*klick* I.  Am.  Totally.  Going.  To.  Set.  You.  Jerkfaces.  On.  Fire. *klang*"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3277389925" "You've.  Got.  To.  Help.  Flambeaux.  {HeroName}.  *clunk*  Help.  Me.  And.  I.  Help.  You."
