// IntroString :
"P1320094263" "This should be pretty straightforward.  Take the sub to Peregrine Island in Paragon City, sneak into the sewers, locate the artifact that your contact told you about and get out of there.  This Rikti Artifact will cause the Rikti to go berserk while trying to find this artifact.  This will cause untold damage as well as serving as a great distraction."
// AcceptString :
"P2486803571" "Activate the Rikti Artifact to cause mayhem."
// SendOffString :
"P3610018996" "As if causing destruction in Paragon City isn't incentive enough, this could also create a distraction that will allow you to carry out other plans unnoticed for a short time.  You head off towards the sub that will take you to Paragon City."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P723902595" "Activate Rikti Artifact"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P681333435" "Somewhere in Peregrine Island there's a Rikti artifact just waiting to be activated.  All you have to do is get to Paragon City."
// TaskTitle :
"P4290180208" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Rikti Artifact Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P635578754" "You can hear the sirens of police drones and the muffled sounds of voices speaking over a communicator.  Deeper in the sewer tunnels you can hear a heated argument."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3682182595" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Rikti Artifact Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Your distraction worked as intended.  As soon as the artifact was activated Rikti started pouring into the area and causing mayhem.  The heroes in the area won't know what hit them."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3995323621" "Are you kidding me?<em t=2>What do you mean they won't let us in here?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P366323010" "<em t=1>You heard me.<em t=3>Those Paragon Police idiots are giving Officer Deegan a seriously hard time."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3968025157" "Look at what the Paragon Police's stalling has allowed to happen!  Villain trouble!"

