// Dialog :
"P3596693150" "You found something."
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1155275023" "Artifact: Located!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3936400553" "Priority: Artifact Procurement."
// Script Variable ACTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2985593368" "Thieves: Eliminate!"
// Script Variable NEGOTIATOR_ONE_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P2459581029" "You can't just waltz in here.<em t=2>This artifact is under our jurisdiction.  It's time for you to take a hike."
// Script Variable NEGOTIATOR_ONE_ATTACK_TEXT :
"P2634265967" "<em t=3>We could have had this...thing...safely removed from here by now if it wasn't for your meddling, Deegan!"
// Script Variable NEGOTIATOR_TWO_INACTIVE_TEXT :
"P1596650601" "Whoa!  Whoa!<em t=1>I don't think so.<em t=2>This is clearly an alien artifact here and I believe that falls under our jurisdiction.  Not yours."
