// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - RiktiTechClue1 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P583644489" "Rikti Medicine"
// DetailString :
"P2489909066" "This crate contains Rikti medical supplies.  Who knows what they'd do to a human?  Maybe cure cancer, perhaps give you cancer, or maybe cause you to grow an extra limb.  Doesn't matter to you, as long as someone's willing to pay you a boatload of cash for them."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - RiktiTechClue2 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2098108953" "The Motherlode"
// DetailString :
"P2094370924" "Now, this is what you're talking about!  A crate loaded to the brim with small, unrecognizable gadgets that look expensive and have half a dozen flashing lights on them.  These will likely sell for a small fortune."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - RiktiTechClue3 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P390576766" "Rikti Cooking Tools"
// DetailString :
"P2324372355" "You stumble upon what appear to be Rikti cooking devices.  You sift through a number of items that catch your interest, one that catches your eye is something that appear to be an alien egg beater, but with way too many extra attachments."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3448239565" "The plan is simple.  Spread some rumors about the Rikti Artifact, hitch a ride to Paragon City on a sub, wait for someone to activate it and wait for mayhem to ensue.  Then, you're free to hit up that Rikti base and procure not one, but hopefully several Rikti Artifacts!"
// AcceptString :
"P3098074603" "Wait for the Artifact to be activated, then go loot the Rikti base."
// SendOffString :
"P3082562354" "You've spread the rumors. Any time now someone should try to activate the artifact.  It's time to set off to Paragon City and raid that Rikti base.  You head off to catch a ride to Paragon City.  You can almost smell the cash you'll make after you sell those Rikti devices."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P231818929" "Loot the Rikti Base"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1175280059" "Somewhere in Peregrine Island is a Rikti base loaded with goodies... all with your name on them.  You just need to get to the submarine and head over there."
// TaskTitle :
"P938531319" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Rikti Artifact Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3292099556" "The odd hum of alien technology buzzes in your ear.  Normally, it would be irritating, but today it sounds like money."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2876921325" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Rikti Artifact Rumors</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>What a haul!  You knew someone would go after that Rikti Artifact, which gave you the perfect opportunity to see where the Rikti raiders were coming from.  That lead you this Rikti base, which you picked clean."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3323139878" "Base: Vulnerability: High"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2504944391" "Guard duty: Always."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3247949092" "Fun: Killing intruders!"

