// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL8-9_Task_16 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Point 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P3417983099" "Hollow Point's Nation"
// DetailString :
"P253919612" "You found a datapad off of an Arachnos operative which detailed their fight against Hollow Point. It would seem he has gathered a surprising amount of followers for his army and has actually become a serious threat to some parts of Arachnos.<br><br>The datapad notes some rumors that Hollow Point may even be in talks with Marshal Blitz about combining the forces of their two armies."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Ceasefire 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P2738894606" "Truce! Truce!"
// DetailString :
"P1014772107" "Before you could finish off the Arachnos lackeys, they asked what you were doing here. You decided to humor them by divulging the true reason you were here. When they learned why you were here, they actually become rather amiable, saying they would call off the other soldiers and allow you to pass through to get the Nullifier gun.<br><br>It looks like Arachnos doesn't even want to use the gun all that much."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P387620341" "You're not too interested in Lt. Demitrovich's payment for the new Nullifier Gun MK II. However, if she plans on giving the schematics to Longbow, you don't see why you couldn't...have some fun with this.<br><br>She wouldn't know, of course, about the additions you made to it - neither would Longbow, until their Nullifiers suddenly get a face full of fire when they try to use the guns. And then...who will Demitrovich blame? The villain who <i>sold</i> her the Nullifier Gun? Or Arachnos, who originally got their hands on the gun <i>from</i> Demitrovich?"
// AcceptString :
"P1803597596" "Modify the Nullifier Gun MK II Schematics!"
// SendOffString :
"P3170437506" "You figure out that Arachnos is keeping the schematics inside of one of their bases in Grandville. While outsiders might think this would be an impossible task to handle, you know differently - it'll be all too easy getting inside of that base."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3518431051" "Trick Lt. Demitrovich!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3322884425" "You'll have to try to get a video of Demitrovich's reaction when those guns begin to blow up."
// TaskTitle :
"P2699533129" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Old Russian Ballad</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P3350846963" "Just another typical Arachnos base - you're fairly used to them by now. The schematics are in here, somewhere - probably poorly guarded at that."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P2479187100" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Old Russian Ballad</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You modified the schematics and delivered them to Lt. Demitrovich. She was very appreciative of your help and said she would deliver the information to Longbow right away. <br><br>Perfect."
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1803041734" "You'll die for the sake of my toaster! <em t=2> And YOU! This will be for the radio! <em t=3> And then HE'LL be for the goggles...<em t=3> And her...ohhh...she's cunning, for what she did to the boots...<em t=3> But that one man...I won't forgive him for what he did...<em t=3>...to my remote control. <em t=3> Ahahahaha!"
// Script Variable HOSTAGE_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3130940930" "Ohhh, {HeroName}! <em t=3>You fight on behalf of my toaster?"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3693256205" ".... <em t=8> You're out of your mind!"
// Script Variable CAPTOR_ACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3592853531" "Why do problems keep cropping up all around us?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P4273719940" "Bane Spider Executioner"
// Script Variable SayOnRescue :
"P3307493138" "Huh? Nullifier Gun? <em t=3> I'm just here to get some vengeance for my utilities! <em t=2> But I guess if you're here too, I could tag along. Let's upset the established order! <em t=2>For my toothbrush!"

