// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P1125845029" "I saw some Longbow Nullifiers holding up a villain before - they went to fire and their guns blew up! It was horrifying!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_16 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Ajax 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P4107947481" "Ajax's Background"
// DetailString :
"P1889134232" "You found a file that Malta had on the hero Ajax...<br><br>REAL NAME: Ralph Valetti<br><br>FORMER OCCUPATION: Ex-Con<br><br>CURRENT ACTIVITIES: Wallowing in self-pity.<br><br>PROPOSAL: Observation for now, wait for more activity."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Treatment 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P99107262" "Shock Treatment's Background"
// DetailString :
"P3559800824" "You found a file that Malta had on the villain Shock Treatment...<br><br>REAL NAME: Rebecca Holister<br><br>FORMER OCCUPATION: Research Assistant<br><br>CURRENT ACTIVITIES: Spreading chaos and destruction throughout the Rogue Isles<br><br>PROPOSAL: Keep eye on her, reel her in when she becomes too much of a liability."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Plethora 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P1951519008" "Lt. Demitrovich's Background"
// DetailString :
"P478087340" "You found the Malta file regarding Lt. Demitrovich...<br><br>REAL NAME: Demitrovich (First name unknown)<br><br>FORMER OCCUPATION: Russian Freedom Fighter<br><br>CURRENT OCUPATION: Longbow Lieutenant<br><br>CURRENT ACTIVITIES: Double-crossing Longbow on multiple accounts - images, recordings, and other physical evidence can be seen on pages 5 through 30 of report attached.<br><br>PROPOSAL: Allow her to continue to subvert Longbow, ensure she does not try to cross Malta."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue - Longbow 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Clue Name :
"P502981272" "The Longbow Deal"
// DetailString :
"P3297877275" "You contacted Longbow regarding a certain Lt. Demitrovich, saying that you had hard evidence regarding some...less than honest deals she was in. Longbow requested the information, at which point you requested the proper fee for it.<br><br>After some haggling and convincing, Longbow agreed to pay you, wiring the amount you requested to your person. Once that was done, you sent them a copy of the file you found.<br><br>With that complete, you contacted Lt. Demitrovich, requesting she meet you in the base to discuss 'matters pertaining to her actions in the Rogue Isles'. Time to make some more money."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3818216190" "Dobreden, {HeroName}. So you wish to speak to me about my dealings.<br><br>I suppose you've heard of my plans to retrieve the MK II Nullifier Gun.<br><br>So...do you have the schematics?"
// Answer Text :
"P1603805930" "No. Actually, I'm not here about that."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P946292569" "<color orange>Lt. Demitrovich tilts her head curiously.</color><br><br>Then what are you here for? I assume this isn't a call to just say hello to me..."
// Answer Text :
"P4061587864" "(Explain to Demitrovich that you have all the files to blackmail her.)"
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3330821312" "<color orange>Lt. Demitrovich remains silent for a moment, her lip twisting in anger. She takes a breath, calming herself.</color><br><br>...I see. I suppose I should not be surprised that...Malta had this information on me. And that you now have it.<br><br>I can only imagine that if you're telling me this, you intend use this to gain some money from me in exchange for your silence, correct?"
// Answer Text :
"P3317351794" "That would be right. (Name your price)"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P4255561698" "...you ask for a steep amount, {HeroName}. But...I suppose it is worth it. One moment...<br><br><color orange>Lt. Demitrovich picks up her phone, making a call. The two of you stand in awkward silence for a few moments before a man in a duster hat arrives, carrying a suitcase. The man quickly leaves. Demitrovich hands you the suitcase.</color><br><br>This should have everything you need. And now...I would appreciate it if you would give me those documents."
// Answer Text :
"P1128270583" "Sure, you can have this copy."
// Answer Text :
"P804001175" "(Hand her the copy without telling her about Longbow)"
// Page Copy Text :
"P1844146044" "<color orange>You hand the files over to Demitrovich, who takes them with a suspicious eye.</color><br><br>You said...copy? What exactly do you mean by that?"
// Answer Text :
"P4063785124" "Oh, right, I gave the other copy to Longbow."
// Page Orly Text :
"P2725609970" "You little...!<br><br><color orange>Demitrovich goes to draw out her pistol.</color><br><br>I'll kill you for this, {HeroName}!"
// Answer Text :
"P2571510673" "Before you do, I'd like you to take a moment to consider something."
// Page Yarly Text :
"P4014738207" "You have two seconds before I blow your brains out.<br><br><color orange>You explain to Lt. Demitrovich the current situation. Which is that you just waded through a <i>Malta</i> base in order to get this information, taking down multiple agents of the secret paramilitary organization that make most super-powered beings terrified when they even think about fighting them. You then ask Demitrovich that, with that in mind, how exactly does she, a sole operative within Longbow, armed with a pistol, exactly intend on taking you down?<br><br>You reassure Demitrovich by telling her that she's by all means welcome to try, but that it's advisable to just walk away from the situation at hand.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3482325228" "...and there you go."
// Page Pwned Text :
"P1132171999" "<color orange>Lt. Demitrovich slowly puts her gun away. Without another word, she turns and walks off with her tail between her legs, leaving you with your case full of money.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2044936972" "Good choice, Demitrovich."
// Page Trick Text :
"P2501745946" "<color orange>You give Demitrovich all the evidence to be used against her. She smiles at you, nodding her head.</color><br><br>I'm glad we could come to this arrangement, {HeroName}. Perhaps now that you know of my dealings, we could work something out in the future. I could always use a {Hero.gender=male man|woman} of your talents."
// Answer Text :
"P268146804" "Sure, I wouldn't mind that at all."
// Page Fool Text :
"P3741464078" "<color orange>Lt. Demitrovich shakes your hand before she walks out of the base. She won't know that Longbow now knows her dirty secrets - not until it's too late, of course.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P2044893163" "Now, what to spend this money on..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2440412704" "Lt. Demitrovich is a woman who closely guards all of her secrets - from the villains she deals with in the Isles and from the soldiers she serves with in Longbow. You're sure that the people in Longbow would be <i>very</i> generous in their payment for outing a traitor in their group.<br><br>You're also certain that Demitrovich would be willing to pay a good amount of money to keep her secrets safe. As long as she doesn't know about Longbow having the information until it's too late for her to do anything about it.<br><br>It's just a matter of tracking down the evidence to present to Longbow."
// AcceptString :
"P3843938486" "Get the blackmail information on Demitrovich!"
// SendOffString :
"P559371078" "After doing some extensive research, you find out, to your dismay, that the one group who has all the information regarding Demitrovich's activities are...<i>Malta</i>. Of course.<br><br>Looks like you'll really be earning your money today."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P2470392153" "Retrieve blackmail information!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3524870611" "You'll be interested in seeing Demitrovich's face once she realizes all of her secrets are now public."
// TaskTitle :
"P1755971728" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Old Russian Ballad</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P2613690461" "The Malta warehouse is bustling with activity. There's a lot of information here on the people they're tracking, though you're only after what they have for Lt. Demitrovich."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3408343297" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Old Russian Ballad</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Sometimes the best way to make a profit is to play all the sides that are involved. Longbow will no doubt be after the good lieutenant now. While she's on the run, you'll be sure to be spending all that money she so...graciously gave to you."
// Script Variable NPC_DIALOG_NAME :
"P3985914409" "Lt. Demitrovich"

