// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2496510268" "We'll have to try to get some of our people into Praetoria, somehow."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P1084338221" "Do we give aid to the resistance or no?"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1225327618" "I'm wary of all of them in Praetoria. Let 'em all burn, that's what I say."

