// Clue Name :
"P1495722441" "Rikti Technology"
// DetailString :
"P2084199415" "You found a large amount of powerful Rikti technology within the Traditionalist base. Teleporters, plasma cannons, Rikti powered combat gloves, large Rikti swords - enough to supply a small army of Rikti.<br><br>Of course, now it's all in <i>your</i> hands."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Flam 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P332448085" "Okay! Hold on! I give up! Look...{HeroName}...why don't we cut a deal? The two of us?"
// Answer Text :
"P1530221768" "I'm listening..."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P3430490737" "I stop fighting you...and -you- will graciously allow me to come with you and take the glory in blowing up this base!"
// Answer Text :
"P3972543004" "I actually have a better idea."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P3848779957" "What...what's the idea?"
// Answer Text :
"P2650874663" "I beat you to a pulp and you learn not to cross me again!"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P3054579700" "Fine, if that's how it's going to be, {HeroName}!"
// Answer Text :
"P3845852197" "It is how it's going to be!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3725749503" "Traditionalists...Restructurists...does it really matter what name they call the Rikti? Not to you, at least - you look at them and all you see is an opportunity. From what you've discovered, this Traditionalist base will be packed with Rikti technology - and possibly information. Vanguard won't be guarding it, as it's outside of the limits of their influence.<br><br>Which means that it's just sitting there...waiting for someone to walk in and take whatever is in that base for themselves."
// AcceptString :
"P4264329403" "Rob and destroy the Rikti base!"
// SendOffString :
"P474433999" "You head off towards the Traditionalist base. Hopefully no one else has gone there before you - if so, you'll just have to...<color red>inform</color> them that this base is <i>yours</i> for the picking."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P4111137560" "Destroy the Traditionalist Base!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3115965555" "If Vanguard shows up, you'll just show them what happens if they try to get in the way of what you want."
// TaskTitle :
"P2244708812" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Wanted: Uqua. Dead: Alive</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4274318434" "You can hear the light hum of Rikti technology throughout the cavern. You're close to their main base."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P3561562324" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Wanted: Uqua. Dead: Alive</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You run out from the Rikti base with all of the stolen technology you found. Moments later, a large burst of fire erupts from underneath the ground, shooting out like a spurt from the hole you crawled out of. Nothing is left in that base now - including evidence that you were ever there."
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3090575977" "Begin: Hunt. Target: Hostile Rikti"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1088668970" "{HeroName}:Curious. Truly wish: hostilities?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Polar 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P402960151" "<shout>This is MY base to destroy, {HeroName}, not yours!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P992783998" "Looks like I've gotta show you what happens when someone gets in my way!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P462333296" "Are you feeling it yet? Huh?! Huh?!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2618797838" "When I blow up this place, EVERYONE is gonna have to recognize what I can do!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P640238854" "Erk! W-whoa whoa, okay okay! H-hold on! <em t=1> Just kidding!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P508160723" "E-erk! Not really!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4064906795" "I'll remember this...when I'm burning you down...in the future..."
// Script Variable OBJECT_DISPLAYNAME :
"P530922472" "Rikti Supplies"
// Script Variable ACTOR_GUARDING_DIALOG :
"P4033125346" "Supplies: Crucial"
// Script Variable ACTOR_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P871888125" "{HeroName}: Restructurist Spy?"

