"P2382158232" "Serpent Drummer looked furious in that interview he gave the other day! Looks like something set back peace negotiations with the Traditionalists!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_17 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - DialogTree 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P3577155803" "So, {HeroName}. I can see that you have made it through. <br><br>You must have: questions. Unfortunately I will not give you the answers you seek.  I warn you right now.<br><br>I'm giving you: last chance to walk away."
// Answer Text :
"P1283220738" "Not going to happen Uqua. This is business."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P496066382" "What if I put: counter-offer to you?<br><br>I will pay you: more than highest bidder."
// Answer Text :
"P262131876" "I don't really trust a shape-shifting Rikti working for Crey."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P1648637470" "That is a fault: your own.<br><br>It will be, as the humans say, your funeral."
// Answer Text :
"P4057976916" "I doubt that."
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1207031181" "Kill {HeroName}!"
// Answer Text :
"P4126636940" "Let's go!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P596964087" "You've seen Kelly Uqua give several interviews on behalf of Crey. The look in her eyes has always made people uncomfortable - as if she was some sort of alien. It's quite frankly not too surprising to hear that she may actually be a Rikti in disguise - though it is a little disconcerting that the Rikti could disguise themselves as humans.<br><br>Regardless, there's a bounty out on her head, and you're not going to let something like the possibility of going through Crey get in your way!"
// AcceptString :
"P598544005" "Collect the bounty on Kelly Uqua!"
// SendOffString :
"P3258986450" "You do some investigation to find out where Kelly Uqua should be - within one of Crey's offices, right in the heart of Grandville."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1836858403" "Bring in Kelly Uqua!"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P1844855426" "Whenever Crey is involved, you know you're bound to step into something disturbing."
// TaskTitle :
"P4116536109" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Wanted: Uqua. Dead: Alive</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P172763235" "Crey has this office on full lockdown - it looks like they're well aware that the Traditionalists are out to bring Kelly Uqua in."
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1778665328" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>Wanted: Uqua. Dead:Alive</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>You drag Kelly Uqua to the nearest soldier in Vanguard. They know right away what you're there for, taking in Kelly Uqua, while handing you a card to claim your bounty. It seems they were <i>quite</i> serious about finding Uqua, as the card was actually a key to a large warehouse full of various pieces of technology! You'll have to do work for the Vanguard, or Traditionalists for that matter, more often!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2761180336" "We can't let anyone get to Uqua, not in the condition she's currently in."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P105987010" "It's {HeroName}! Put the base on full alert!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P3484887429" "Who would be foolish enough to try to collect the bounty on her?"
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1728946348" "Great...!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P2428906841" "We've almost shut down all the investigations that Raymond was doing regarding Uqua."
// Script Variable ATTACK_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P2453317635" "Looks like we should have focused more on {HeroName}...!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION1 :
"P3607248458" "You're going to wish you never came here, {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable INACTIVE_DIALOG_MINION2 :
"P1911370126" "Call in the Deathstalker!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - Deathstalker 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P2960139583" "Scorpinoid Deathstalker"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P626904582" "<shout>Signal received. Moving to intercept {HeroName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3801984378" "Kel'Uqua"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P1189950795" "This is the true form of Kelly Uqua, a Rikti who had themselves transformed into a human in order to be of use to Crey industries!"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3527315961" "This isn't good. The transformation effect is losing: effectiveness."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P3280038874" "I gave you one last chance. Now I must deliver: death!"
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P1246985753" "<em victory>I expected more from you, {HeroName}."

