"P254161185" "Wow... Kelly Uqua... I would have never guessed..."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Vil_SL8-9_Task_18 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Caernoz 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P284435460" "So... You bring tribute before me, do you?  Or is this some delusion of grandeur you possess... A plot to banish me, like that pathetic whelp, Desdemona?"
// Answer Text :
"P1277825962" "This is a gift, Lord Caernoz."
// Page InformationPage1 Text :
"P1027843769" "So you bring me a toy as a gift, do you? A paltry trinket is your tribute? And what is going on within that small mind of yours?  Dreams of power in return?"
// Answer Text :
"P4293333020" "Actually, yes. I want power in exchange for the dagger."
// Page InformationPage2 Text :
"P453739058" "You dare haggle with me as if I were some street pedder in cheap wares?! Very well, {VillainName}, if you wish a reward then I shall grant it.  For your impertinance, I grant you..."
// Answer Text :
"P3720851344" "Continue"
// Page InformationPage3 Text :
"P1870700085" "... Eternal suffering!!!"
// Answer Text :
"P3898145311" "Close"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P2884392419" "Having once been a demon-summoner filled with an unholy hatred towards all caped do-gooders, Desdemona's change of heart is rather... upsetting.  Now it seems that she's managed to convince other people of her noble intentions, enough that they're willing to give her such a powerful object to *STOP* demons?  No... she's gone too far this time.<br><br>Instead of just watching her grisly end at the hands of this powerful demonic entity, why not add to her failure by presenting this dagger to that demonic beast?<br><br>Who knows?  Maybe it might grant you a reward in the process."
// AcceptString :
"P3568969302" "Stop Desdemona from sealing the Demon's portal"
// SendOffString :
"P1869968637" "You have a pretty good idea where Desdemona might have gone.  If you make it there in time, you just might be able to finish her off personally.  The look on her face will be all the more delightful once you present this dagger to her demonic foe."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P3154493693" "Return the dagger to Caernoz"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3142751918" "If you're going to get any kind of reward from this demon prince, you're going to need to stop Desdemona from sealing him away forever!"
// TaskTitle :
"P2323388704" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Dagger of Caernoz</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Villain Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P4028445305" "You're pretty certain this is the place Desdemona plans on facing off against the demon Caernoz.  If you track down Desdemona before she finds out her plan isn't going to work, you may get to beat her face in yourself!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1680096356" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Dagger of Caernoz</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Red><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>Although you managed to humiliate Desdemona by defeating her in combat, you earned a new enemy by the name of Lord Caernoz, an infernal demon from the depths below.<br><br>Word of that is sure to spread like wildfire, and they'll all know it was *YOU*!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3235160180" "Desdemona - former demon-summoner for the side of evil, now an agent for the forces of good.  Rather than using her talents to bind demons into her service, she is now attempting to seal away a demon lord."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P3606310576" "With the power of Caernoz's very own dagger, I'll be able to forever seal away this unholy terror!"
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1321806701" "{VillainName}?  Do not tell me that you are now in the employ of this deceitful one?<em t=3>I thought even you had some standards!"
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P2180050309" "You can not stop me, {VillainName}.<em t=3>Tell your lord that he will no longer hold this world in his inhuman grip!"
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3041983450" "What you don't know is that this dagger works on his minions just as much as him!<em t=3>This means you, {VillainName}!"
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1186567183" "What is wrong here... Why is the dagger not banishing you to the nether realms!?"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1574356243" "Why... Why do you also possess the dagger?<em t=3>*gasp*<em t=3>This one I'm holding... it... it's false..."
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P262684883" "No... {VillainName}... Don't do this.<em t=3>Caernoz's only reward given to his minions is a cold, unending death..."
// Script Variable BOSS_KILLEDHERO_DIALOG :
"P362658566" "It didn't have to end this way."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P1738482053" "Nevermind"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptDesdemonaDefeated 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P371171633" "Find and defeat Desdemona"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P1411189644" "You have defeated Desdemona."
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYNAME :
"P3049889964" "Lord Caernoz"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P172875473" "Lord Caernoz, a demon lord most foul, has taken the host of a Death Mage to house his manifestion upon this world.  Any mortal form less powerful would slowly melt away under the sheer greatness of his presence."
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P1048010907" "I sense you, mortal.<em t=3>Creeping among the detritus of these foul halls...<em t=3>The scent of corruption gives you away...<br><br>...stand before me, {VillainName}."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3239975874" "You presumed too much."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P902794737" "You think to defeat me, but you are sorely mistaken."
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P3241514696" "As long as my altar stands, my supplicants will bring me into this world again and again!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DEAD_DIALOG :
"P4060585121" "You have delayed me, {VillainName}, but not stopped me.<em t=3>I will see you shortly."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P4016516949" "Feel my wrath, mortal!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptChangeTeam 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P3402898902" "Present Lord Caernoz his dagger"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P333210624" "You have defeated Lord Caernoz."
// Script Variable OBJECT_DISPLAYNAME :
"P1771751420" "Summoning Altar of Caernoz"
// Script Variable ACTOR_GUARDING_DIALOG :
"P24586386" "Protect the passageway of Lord Caernoz with your lives!<em t=3>He shall tear our souls from our corpses if we fail!"
// Script Variable ACTOR_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P1694320659" "You will not leave here with your soul, unbeliever!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptCaernozAltar 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P1327917158" "Destroy Lord Caernoz's Altar before he returns!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P555863662" "You have prevented Lord Caernoz from returning through the portal... For now."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - TaskSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P3123143372" "You've destroyed the altar of Lord Caernoz.  Now get out of here before his worshippers get more ticked off than they already are!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - ReturnSuccess 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// RandomFameString :
"P282910567" "Whoa... I heard {VillainName} squared off against some demon lord and won.  How's that for a reputation, eh?"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task - AM_Rog_SL8-9_Task_18 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog - Desdemona 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Page Intro Text :
"P4041113829" "You have no idea what kind of power you're meddling with, {VillainName}.  Caernoz does not reward his minions with the treasures he promises.  All of his tempting offers are nothing but lies, and only in the end will you see that you're nothing more than what you started out as... a pawn."
// Answer Text :
"P3024152400" "I'm not working for the guy.  I'm here to make you an offer."
// Page DesTradeOne Text :
"P1187115333" "You're here to make me an offer?  Like Caernoz, I'm assuming?  Come 'back' to the life I used to live, one filled with anger and hatred?  A life dedicated to bringing pain and suffering to those I thought wronged me?<br><br>No.<br><br>I will never return to that hollow life.  Kill me if you must, but I will die redeemed."
// Answer Text :
"P1807621129" "Actually, I'm here to trade you this dagger to stop Caernoz."
// Page DesTradeTwo Text :
"P2760352754" "You're here to help?  Do you honestly expect me to believe something like that?  But... You being here makes no sense... Give me a moment to think.<br><br><color orange>Desdemona stares at you for a moment, as if she's considering a weighty choice.  With a nod more to herself than to you, she begins speaking again.</color><br><br>Alright then... I'll speak with Freedom Phalanx and tell them that you helped when you could have harmed.  If a reward is what you want, you'll get it.  HOWEVER..."
// Answer Text :
"P2087849433" "Why did I know it wasn't going to be quick?"
// Page DesTradeThree Text :
"P144688999" "I could have taken the dagger from you as we were talking, but remember that I'm one of the good guys.  We do things the right way.  So if you want to do this right, then you're going to help me seal Caernoz's summoning portal while I take care of his mortal shell.  Once you've closed it, meet me further into this labyrinth and I'll... ugh... pay you.<br><br><color orange>Desdemona extends her hand in a gesture implying she wants to shake hands on the deal.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P1497154210" "Fine...  Just make sure the reward is worth it."
// Page DesTradeFour Text :
"P2404158408" "<color orange>You and Desdemona shake hands.</color>"
// Answer Text :
"P3189142790" "[Close]"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Task Header Items 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// IntroString :
"P3666438435" "Having once been a demon-summoner filled with an unholy hatred towards all caped do-gooders, Desdemona's change of heart is something that doesn't really concern you in the least.  If she wants to go the holier-than-thou route, that's entirely up to her.  According to this message, it appears she's about to face off against some demon or devil or whatever boogeyman she thinks she needs to fight.  But seeing as you're the one with the object she needs to pull this off, you've got the upper hand when it comes to... negotiating a deal.<br><br>It would benefit you a lot more to let her succeed rather than watch her painfully die.  When the day's done, she'll stop that demon of hers and you'll walk away with a fat sack of cash!"
// AcceptString :
"P2442217077" "Trade with Desdemona before she gets herself killed!"
// SendOffString :
"P147841968" "You have a pretty good idea where Desdemona might have gone.  If you make it there in time, you just might be able to make a deal with her before that demon winds up eviscerating the girl.  Remember, she's in no position to make any demands."
// ActiveTaskString :
"P1497176958" "Make a deal with Desdemona"
// YoureStillBusyString :
"P3950227941" "If you're going to make some money off of this situation, you're going to need to talk with Desdemona before she's finished!"
// TaskTitle :
"P1559118574" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Dagger of Caernoz</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Rogue Mission</i></color></span>"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// MissionDef 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// EntryString :
"P391030607" "You're pretty certain this is the place Desdemona plans on facing off against the demon Caernoz.  If you track down Desdemona before she finds out her plan isn't going to work, you may make yourself some fast, easy cash!"
// ExitStringSuccess :
"P1966793868" "<font face=title><scale 1.1><span align=center><color orange>The Dagger of Caernoz</color></span></scale></font><br><span align=center><color Yellow><i>Alignment Mission</i></color></span><br><br>After all the work you did to help that idiot of a demon summoner, all you got for it was a high-and-mighty speech about turning your life around.<br><br>That's the last time you'll work out a deal with someone without seeing the cash FIRST!"
// Script Variable BOSS_DISPLAYINFO :
"P3216886219" "Desdemona, former demon-summoner for the side of evil, now an agent for the forces of good.  Rather than using her talents to bind demons into her service, she is now attempting to seal away a demon lord."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P78860338" "Stop! I yield to you, {VillainName}.  Before you finish me, at least tell me why you joined forces with Caernoz."
// Script Variable SaysList :
"P2047411700" "Now seal that portal while I'm personally taking care of Caernoz."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptDesdemonaExits 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P1994057231" "Find and work out a deal with Desdemona"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P597603489" "You have worked out a deal with Desdemona."

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Objective - ScriptCaernozAltar 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Description :
"P2305339194" "Destroy Lord Caernoz's Altar While Desdemona Fights Him!"

// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Reward - Objective 
// -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
// Dialog :
"P1478310614" "You have sealed Caernoz's portal... Now it's time to get your reward!"
// Script Variable BOSS_INACTIVE_DIALOG :
"P2132339544" "{VillainName}!  I'm over here.  It's time for your reward."
// Script Variable BOSS_ATTACK_DIALOG :
"P2854117847" "Remember me telling you we heroes do things the right way?<em t=3>Well, the right way is that you'll need to pay for your crimes before you can collect any kind of reward."
// Script Variable BOSS_1STBLOOD_DIALOG :
"P2125123462" "I know it sounds like I'm betraying you, but I'm not.<em t=3>Once you've done your time, I will see to it personally you get your money."
// Script Variable BOSS_75HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P1601601526" "{VillainName}, please listen.  This is your one chance to turn things around for yourself.<em t=3>I did it, and I know you can, too."
// Script Variable BOSS_50HEALTH_DIALOG :
"P2087884954" "Stop fighting!  I'm actually trying to help you here!"
// Script Variable BOSS_25HEALTH_DIALOG :
